{"tid":757363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗過罐頭早發明過罐頭刀 咁之前啲人係點開罐頭？","createTime":"2018-07-26T19:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T21:46:23.000Z","uid":194101,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8045adefc3a0c25955abfc1d1aa64dfbfb6b09be","tid":757363,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說罐頭喺1851年已經發明左<br />\n但係罐頭刀就1873年先有<br />\n咁中間嘅時間啲人點開罐頭<br />\n定係佢地等到1873年先開？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73342ba1503bab0db839541f10d0758a9ed38673","tid":757363,"uid":194101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:29:34.000Z","msg":"請理性討論 多謝大家 真。想知"},{"pid":"2761698aeb38c05cd30bec7dc42621099d2bd88a","tid":757363,"uid":126971,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:31:27.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過點解罐頭擺咁耐先過期，<br />\n就係畀時間你諗下用咩方法開<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3beb9636e7ada3a71d6134096c6a1f954138cc91","tid":757363,"uid":194101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2761698aeb38c05cd30bec7dc42621099d2bd88a","tid":757363,"uid":126971,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T19:31:27.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過點解罐頭擺咁耐先過期，<br />\n就係畀時間你諗下用咩方法開<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/face